msgid "User Installed Packages Help"
msgstr "User Installed Packages Help"

msgid ""
"This application is intended to facilitate the re-installation of packages "
"that the user has added to the default installation."
msgstr ""
"This application is intended to facilitate the re-installation of packages "
"that the user has added to the default installation."

msgid ""
"It can display a list of packages manually installed by the user that can be"
" saved in a simple text file. Furthermore, the application allows loading a "
"saved list of packages for review and selection to be reinstalled. Such a "
"procedure is especially easy and useful after a new system installation."
msgstr ""
"It can display a list of packages manually installed by the user that can be"
" saved in a simple text file. Furthermore, the application allows loading a "
"saved list of packages for review and selection to be reinstalled. Such a "
"procedure is especially easy and useful after a new system installation."

msgid "There are two options to choose from:"
msgstr "There are two options to choose from:"

msgid "quickly and easily create a list of those packages."
msgstr "quickly and easily create a list of those packages."

msgid ""
"use that list in another location to review and reinstall those packages, if"
" still available."
msgstr ""
"use that list in another location to review and reinstall those packages, if"
" still available."

msgid "Create a list of user-installed packages"
msgstr "Create a list of user-installed packages"

msgid "A list of user-installed packages is displayed."
msgstr "A list of user-installed packages is displayed."

msgid ""
"Note: Packages of installed Linux kernels or NVIDIA graphics drivers will "
"not be listed."
msgstr ""
"Note: Packages of installed Linux kernels or NVIDIA graphics drivers will "
"not be listed."

msgid ""
"Press [Save List] and select the location where the package list should be "
"saved."
msgstr ""
"Press [Save List] and select the location where the package list should be "
"saved."

msgid "Open a previously saved list to install selected packages"
msgstr "Open a previously saved list to install selected packages"

msgid "Select the package list you wish to install."
msgstr "Select the package list you wish to install."

msgid ""
"Uncheck any packages in the displayed list that you do not wish to install."
msgstr ""
"Uncheck any packages in the displayed list that you do not wish to install."

msgid ""
"A notification is provided for any missing packages that can no longer be "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"A notification is provided for any missing packages that can no longer be "
"installed."

msgid "Press [OK] and the selected packages will be installed."
msgstr "Press [OK] and the selected packages will be installed."

msgid "Unavailable packages will be listed"
msgstr "Unavailable packages will be listed"

msgid "Packages that are unavailable or uninstallable will be listed."
msgstr "Packages that are unavailable or uninstallable will be listed."

msgid ""
"Such a situation arises when the main package or one of its dependencies can"
" not function within the new system."
msgstr ""
"Such a situation arises when the main package or one of its dependencies can"
" not function within the new system."

msgid ""
"Press [Save List] and select the location to save the list of unavailable "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"Press [Save List] and select the location to save the list of unavailable "
"packages."

msgid "Packages available will be installed"
msgstr "Packages available will be installed"

msgid "The installation process is started within a new terminal window."
msgstr "The installation process is started within a new terminal window."

msgid "Authentication and confirmation are required to perform installation."
msgstr "Authentication and confirmation are required to perform installation."

#. TRANSLATORS:
#. A question "Do you want to continue? [Y/n]" is displayed in the terminal
#. window. The question could be displayed translated, including [Y/N] for
#. translated [Yes/No].
msgid "Press [N] to cancel."
msgstr "Press [N] to cancel."

msgid ""
"To close the terminal window after the installation process finishes, press "
"[Enter]."
msgstr ""
"To close the terminal window after the installation process finishes, press "
"[Enter]."

